<subSubSection id="0C83650EFFE0FF84FF0EFB02FBD9FB02" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="44263685FFE0FF84FF0EFB02FBD9FB02" blockId="7.[174,1232,1153,1372]" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">
Host plants. In 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE0FF84FE54FB02FD9DFB45" box="[441,548,1154,1180]" name="Morocco" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Morocco</collectingCountry>
reared from 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE0FF84FD52FB01FC31FB42" box="[703,904,1153,1179]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Phlomis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fruticosa">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE0FF84FD52FB01FC31FB42" box="[703,904,1153,1179]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Phlomis fruticosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. and 
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE0FF84FC0DFB01FB84FB42" box="[992,1085,1153,1179]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Phlomis</emphasis>
sp., (
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE0FF84FB6FFB01FF52FB65" author="Seguy, E." pageId="7" pageNumber="446" pagination="1 - 206" refId="ref7413" refString="Seguy, E. 1930. Contribution a l'etude des Dipteres du Maroc. Memoire de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physique du Maroc, 24, 1 - 206." type="journal article" year="1930">Séguy, 1930</bibRefCitation>
). Larvae also develop in the FLowers of 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE0FF84FD27FB21FC71FB62" authority="Sieb." authorityName="Sieb." box="[714,968,1185,1211]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Ballota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="saxatilis">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE0FF84FD27FB21FC3FFB62" box="[714,902,1185,1211]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Ballota saxatilis</emphasis>
Sieb.
</taxonomicName>
ex. C. Presl., 
<taxonomicName id="83994D06FFE0FF84FB9EFB21FE87FB02" authority="Poir." authorityName="Poir." class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Phlomis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viscosa">
<emphasis id="76EDEA97FFE0FF84FB9EFB21FF47FB02" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Phlomis viscosa</emphasis>
Poir.
</taxonomicName>
(Lamiaceae) (
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE0FF84FE0EFB41FCA8FB05" author="Freidberg, A. &amp; Kugler, J." box="[483,785,1217,1244]" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" pagination="1 - 212" refId="ref6368" refString="Freidberg, A., Kugler, J. 1989. Fauna Palaestina, Insecta IV, Diptera: Tephritidae. The Israel Academy of Sciences and Humanities, Jerusalem, 1 - 212." type="book chapter" year="1989">Freidberg &amp; Kugler, 1989</bibRefCitation>
) and some other Lamiaceae.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="0C83650EFFE0FF84FF0EFB62FDA4FA85" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="44263685FFE0FF84FF0EFB62FDA4FA85" blockId="7.[174,1232,1153,1372]" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">
D i s t r i b u t i o n. From 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE0FF84FE02FB62FD86FB25" box="[495,575,1250,1276]" name="France" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">France</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE0FF84FD96FB62FD5FFB25" box="[635,742,1250,1276]" name="Morocco" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Morocco</collectingCountry>
to southern East Europe, Caucasus, 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE0FF84FB74FB62FF60FAC2" name="Turkey" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Turkey</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE0FF84FF0AFA81FE9EFAC2" box="[231,295,1281,1307]" name="Israel" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Israel</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE0FF84FE8BFA81FE18FAC2" box="[358,417,1281,1307]" name="Syria" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Syria</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE0FF84FE5EFA82FD4AFAC5" author="Korneyev, V. A. &amp; Dirlbek, J." box="[435,755,1281,1308]" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" pagination="463 - 482" refId="ref6893" refString="Korneyev, V. A., Dirlbek, J. 2001. The fruit flies (Diptera: Tephritidae) of Syria, Jordan and Iraq. Studia Dipterologica, (2000), 7 (2), 463 - 482." type="journal article" year="2001">Korneyev &amp; Dirlbek, 2001</bibRefCitation>
; Korneyev &amp; 
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE0FF84FC77FA82FB9FFAC5" author="Merz, B. &amp; Korneyev, V. A." box="[922,1062,1281,1308]" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" pagination="1" refId="ref7179" refString="Merz, B., Korneyev, V. A. 2004. Tephritidae. In: Pape, T., (ed.), Fauna Europea. Insecta: Diptera. Fauna Europaea version 1. 1, http: // www. faunaeur. org" type="book chapter" year="2004">Merz, 2004</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry id="3C8E7615FFE0FF84FBB2FA82FB75FAC5" box="[1119,1228,1282,1308]" name="Morocco" pageId="7" pageNumber="446">Morocco</collectingCountry>
, this species was collected also in the Middle Atlas in Azrou (
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE0FF84FC85FAA1FC4FFAE5" author="Seguy, E." box="[872,1014,1313,1340]" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" pagination="1 - 206" refId="ref7413" refString="Seguy, E. 1930. Contribution a l'etude des Dipteres du Maroc. Memoire de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physique du Maroc, 24, 1 - 206." type="journal article" year="1930">Séguy, 1930</bibRefCitation>
) and in the coastal meseta in KoriFLa (
<bibRefCitation id="20084B74FFE0FF84FE68FAC1FDA9FA85" author="Seguy, E." box="[389,528,1345,1372]" pageId="7" pageNumber="446" pagination="77 - 92" refId="ref7536" refString="Seguy, E. 1953. Dipteres du Maroc. Encyclopedie Entomologique (B) II. Diptera, 11, 77 - 92." type="journal article" year="1953">Séguy 1953</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
